## 🚀 Quick Start

### Web (Live already at [beaconchain.us](https://beaconchain.us))

To run locally:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/beaconchain-com/Beaconchain.us
cd Beaconchain.us
# open index.html in your browser
```

Mobile (React Native / Expo)

```bash
git clone https://github.com/beaconchain-com/Beaconchain.us
cd Beaconchain.us/mobile   # if separate folder
npm install
npx expo start
```

Backend (Docker – optional)

If you want to run your own beacon chain explorer backend:

```bash
docker pull gobitfly/eth2-beaconchain-explorer
docker run -p 3500:3500 gobitfly/eth2-beaconchain-explorer
```

Requires PostgreSQL and a Prysm beacon node (see full docs).

